Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:14.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:20.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm... Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:25.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I... I finally made it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,His memories returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You won't regret this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello to everyone watching\NOka-chan's co-ed diaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was just dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel really awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're even in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where's Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,His mom and Linda-senpai took him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're heading straight to a local hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:24.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does he really not remember us anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:27.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:35.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It probably fell out of his luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.95,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(288,296)}Golden Time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:19.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:44.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:52.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:03:00.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:08.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:28.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.01,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(535,175)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Horai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.01,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(529,207)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My name is Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The day after I graduated from high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I fell from this bridge, and apparently lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,While my memories were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:09.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,surprisingly, I was attending a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But now that my memories have returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've forgotten everything that happened in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should head home before I catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It looked like a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:33.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I've lost so many important things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,beneath this current.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I submitted a notice of leave of absence to my university.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll probably end up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I found notes to myself in my luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I ran into Linda again there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We were in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(55,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}IMPORTANT PEOPLE WHO MUST NOT BE FORGOTTEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(83,96)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}KAGA KOUKO = EX-GIRLFRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(345,141)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}PROMISED TO PRETEND I FORGOT EVERYTHING BETWEEN US
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(107,235)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}YANAGISAWA MITSUO A.K.A. YANA-SAN,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(62,273)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}GOT MAD WHEN I LIED, DOESN'T LIKE ME ANYMORE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:05:00.49,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(94,294)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}(NEED TO APOLOGIZE WHEN I SEE HIM NEXT)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I even had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But she dumped me. All of this was written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But there's nothing I can clearly recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wonder what my girlfriend looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll find a photo or something if I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:17.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I don't think there's any point in seeing the face of the girl who dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't remember her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.25,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(187,59)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all spam.
