Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.52,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(266,294)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}December 20th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.00,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(54,48)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}From: TADA BANRI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.00,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(95,198)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}To: KAGA KOUKO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I knew the name, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She was the first person mentioned in my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The ex-girlfriend who dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Dear Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm e-mailing you again believing you'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:05.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I would be truly happy if we could spend Christmas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:12.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you still have any feelings for me at all, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget the man you're destined to be with."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I never sent this e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,173)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: To Kouko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,217)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: Don't forget me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,261)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: Destined to love each other
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,295)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: Please message me back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,334)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: Awaiting your response
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(144,373)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko: I'm really worried
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:35.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No responses from Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:42.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I don't know who you are, but stop sending out e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're a nuisance."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:50.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's pretending to be me and trying to get back with a girlfriend I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.64,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(358,78)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}From: Tada Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.64,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(334,135)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}To: Me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.64,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(165,190)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}I won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.64,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(278,235)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}You broke your promise first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:11.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Christmas passed, and Linda came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:14.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Banri, Linda-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:17.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Things got busy, and I forgot about the e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:17.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.56,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(535,157)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Horai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.56,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(529,189)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...the last day of the year arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:28.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should be here on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want to help clean the house, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, is the Tada family pounding mochi this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My dad's been getting stuff ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your dad's going all-out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right! I'll come eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I still love Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:55.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My feelings haven't changed since the day\NI waited for her on that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But Linda hasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:07:59.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're coming over to eat,\NI'll tell my parents to make extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:11.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell them Linda-chan's looking forward to the ones with red bean paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:17.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Because Linda-chan puts toasted mochi with red bean paste in her New Year's soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened between us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,while my memories were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and Linda won't tell me anything.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In fact, isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Lots of people find it gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm still waiting on the bridge for her answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}My family loads ours with seaweed and stock powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:31.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(211,345)}maintaining this balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:31.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(108,310)}She leaves me in the middle of the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even I think that's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:31.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe that's Linda's answer in itself.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ack, that's sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe that's Linda's answer in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I came to return the DVD I borrowed from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,DVD?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were in my notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The Okamera girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Umm... Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oka Chinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're Oka-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oka-chan came from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's Oka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oka Chinami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again, Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:54.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just came to return this DVD to Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not that it's my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is all I came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can see Banri's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have a taxi waiting for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:20.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's in your hands now, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.47,Dialogue11,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(310,309)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}REMEMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:57.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to cross that bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:00.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,the famous wooden bridge, on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, the place where I fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How can I cross that to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can't cross by car,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:17.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so you should have a taxi let you out by the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:21.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can ask him to pick you up on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If my parents were here, we could've given you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're out shopping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:46.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't help much after you came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for the DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:59.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got to see your face again, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:45.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Remember. Remember, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:59.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm broken, shattered, not even close to perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and always lacking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But this is who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I am who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I can go after her if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:40.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I must've given them to you just for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go, Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.30,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(535,157)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Horai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.30,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(529,189)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How come you can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you so wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:36.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How come you can talk to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've always been with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How dare you pretend not to notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You have no idea how frustrated I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:51.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You never listened to anything I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You never even noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:58.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I gave up on everything and decided to stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is this how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll all end up in the same place eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As long as they're alive, everyone's present becomes the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll see you after the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's... "yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's "yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm saying "yes" to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I heard your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I waited all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You dropped something, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:21.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To all of you... my answer is "yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's "yes" to your love for Kouko, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:29.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I can say "yes" to myself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's something I need to take care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You called my name, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:53.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You didn't forget me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was close, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then, what about our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You remember, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You remember, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell me you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I don't forget you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,we'll be together for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know, once this promise is in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,it can never be broken, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:45.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you ever forget me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't show you any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't hold back like I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you until you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you still sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:06.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll never leave you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri... I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop laughing out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:31.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love the time I spend with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love who I am when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,really love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:45.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whether you remember me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wherever I go, wherever I fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:52.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need you to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Without you, I don't know where to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need you, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I made a mistake once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:18.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I just had to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I was holding you back and making you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be free without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be able to change painlessly and naturally without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:39.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But... I couldn't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:44.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Injured, scattered, and incomplete Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And also... my Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to live by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:01.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My heart will always look toward you.
