Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can tell me when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Will you come to my place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes! Let's go home!
